name: Clot
description:
Clot it's been designed to provide easy access to your Video or SLR camera, letting you carry it on either side bag and belt bag modes. It has internal capacity to carry most SLR cameras, Video cameras and it's accessories. 

Designed with an external cover of Neoprene plus EVA, the interior foam assures extra protection to keep your gear safe. It also includes an interior Velcro-adjustable rigid panel divider that lets you organize your equipment your way. Thanks to it's perimetrical zipper the cover can be folded and stored in reduced spaces when it is not in use. 

Interior measures: 23 x 16 x 11 cm
